------------------------------------------------------
FREE Expansion File For Vulcans BURNOUT AGA Amiga Game
------------------------------------------------------

Yes this file is free! Simply Drag to the appropriate drawer
which Burnout Created on your Hard Drive and execute the file
to unpack.

Your Burnout game will instantly recognise the additional Arena
or Car file and it will be available for when next playing.

If you do not yet own Vulcans BURNOUT AGA then see below on how to
order so you can take advantage of the many free expansion files which
will be available from our website or Aminet or Magazine CD's.


