Requirements: AGA Amiga, 2Mb chip + 4Mb fast, Hard Drive.
    Optional: Parallel Port Joystick Adapter (4 Human Players)

              Multi-Play up to 4 players
             100% fully rendered in-game graphics
            Hires Laced 256 Colors @ 25fps
           Stereo High quality Music
          6 Channels of High Definition Sound Effects
         Aura-Interactor Support
        Newtonian Mechanics
       Complex AI for CPU Players
      Mechanics Shop and Weapons
     Full Tournament Arenas
    4 Car Types (Original)
   4 Arenas   (Original)
  4 Bonus Challenges

-------------------------------------------------------------------
Burnout is designed to be totally expandable and Vulcan will be
releasing lots of free extra Cars and Arenas to add to the game,
just like the one you now have.

Burnout will eventually recognise 100 arenas and 33 different cars.

We will also be releasing a free ARENA EDITOR that allows you to load any
IFF graphic into Burnout as an Arena, it will also allow you to add
surface elements such as, ground, plummeting voids, instant death
zones and bounce elements and save with your iff image..

These 'own design arenas' can then be public domain and be swapped and
available over the internet for expanding your Burnout game to the full.




HOW TO ORDER BURNOUT AGA From Vulcans International Mail Order Compnay
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Paying by CHEQUE
----------------
     Make payable to Vulcan Software Limited, the amount must be in
     English Sterling and posted to the address above.

Paying by CREDIT CARD (Access, Mastercard, Visa)
------------------------------------------------
     Either Post, Fax or email us your Credit Card Number along with the
     expiry date.

In all cases please state your full postal address clearly.



